                        <interp inst="t18470705-name-733" type="given" value="JANE"></interp>JANE PARKS</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">being called did not appear.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18470705-name-734" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18470705-name-734" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470705-name-734" type="surname" value="CALLOW"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18470705-name-734" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES CALLOW.</persName>
                  </hi> On the 18th of June female prisoner brought this pair of cloth boots and a pair of shoes to me to sell—I told her they would not</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184707050133"></xptr>
               <p>suit me—she asked if they would suit any of my customers—I told her she might leave them, and I would sell them if I could, and if not she was to take them back again.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Beavan's Defence.</hi> I am innocent of stealing them; I did not know but that they were Finch's property.</p>
